{"name":"Conviction of Error","type":"divineGift","img":"icons/magic/perception/shadow-stealth-eyes-purple.webp","data":{"word":"Deception","description":"Commit Effort. All chosen targets present become convinced that one of their beliefs of your choice is actually a terrible lie that has been imposed upon them, whether it is the existence of a god or the fidelity of their spouse. Worthy foes get a Spirit saving throw. They may reconsider this conviction of error once Effort is reclaimed, but will do so only under great pressure of emotions or obvious facts.","constant":false,"instant":false,"onTurn":false,"action":true,"smite":false,"noEffort":false,"atWill":true,"scene":false,"day":false,"greater":true,"combatPower":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"9kLb9OnQ3UEYBEz7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.zQpYA8RNg3nMNW9k"}},"_id":"3A7IsFC4fwyzr7VB"}
